<li><a href="/wiki/The_Wall_-_Live_in_Berlin" title="The Wall - Live in Berlin">The Wall - Live in Berlin</a>, a rock opera/concert by <a href="/wiki/Roger_Waters" title="Roger Waters">Roger Waters</a> after "The real wall" was torn down. A huge "new wall" made out of bricks was made, then demolished at the end.</li>
</ul>
