ek military junta of 1967–1974">Greek military junta of 1967–1974</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Cultural_Revolution" title="Cultural Revolution">Cultural Revolution</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/1962_Sino-Indian_War" title="1962 Sino-Indian War" class="mw-redirect">1962 Sino-Indian War</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Prague_Spring" title="Prague Spring">Prague Spring</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Goulash_Communism" title="Goulash Communism">Goulash Communism</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sino-Soviet_border_conflict" title="Sino-Soviet border conflict">Sino-Soviet border conflict</a></div>
